===2013 season=== The 2013 Honkbal Hoofdklasse season began on April 11, 2013. Mampaey The Hawks from Dordrecht competed in the Hoofdklasse for the first time. Sparta/Feyenoord, the relegated team from the 2012 season, was declared bankrupt by the Rotterdam court on November 22, 2012<ref>http://insolventies.rechtspraak.nl/pdf.ashx?ID=rot.12.821.F.V.01</ref> and did not compete in the Overgangsklasse.
