{{For|the stadium in Morogoro|Jamhuri Stadium (Morogoro)}}

The '''Jamhuri Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Dodoma]], [[Tanzania]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and serves as the home venue for [[JKT Ruvu Stars]].  It holds 10,000 people.

